    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC《历代危害》的内容也已包含：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在巅峰时期对抗历史性疾病！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在弹幕风格的挑战中，面对强大的Boss！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一场战斗都将考验你的适应能力、技巧和策略思维，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为你很脆弱，需要管理耐力，通过冲刺躲避高速动作中的攻击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而要进步，你不仅需要击败它们，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还要掌握战斗以获取最高排名，并获得解锁更多战斗所需的星星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过基因改造自定义你的病毒：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想更快？更具攻击性？更具韧性？选择由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ 个基于现实微生物的Boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高难度Boss战，强调闪避与耐力管理</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >额外游戏模式（无限Roguelite、街机模式）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个Boss都有专属配乐，充满能量，将鼓与贝斯融合，并包含多种电子音乐风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种装备选项：头部（射击）、腿部（冲刺）、身体（被动技能），深刻改变玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ 个辅助小病毒，提供多样功能助战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好踏入这场微观冒险，但小心——别被彻底消灭了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
